---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "2026-06-02";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Creative Journey"
  description="Terms & Conditions for Creative Journey, including our SMS alert program terms."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-primary py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
            Terms &amp; Conditions
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">
            Last updated: {lastUpdated}
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Terms Content -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-lg">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-8">
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">1. Acceptance of these terms</h2>
              <p>
                These Terms &amp; Conditions ("Terms") govern your access to and use of Creative
                Journey (the "Service"). By creating an account or using the Service, you agree to be
                bound by these Terms. If you don't agree, please don't use the Service.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">2. The Service</h2>
              <p>
                Creative Journey provides a signed-in dashboard for tracking watchlists, recording
                paper trades, and surfacing market patterns on tickers you follow. The Service is for
                informational and educational purposes only and does not constitute financial,
                investment, or trading advice. You are solely responsible for any decisions you make.
                We make no guarantee as to the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of any market
                data or signal.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. Accounts</h2>
              <p>
                Sign-in is handled through GitHub or Google OAuth. You're responsible for activity
                under your account and for keeping your OAuth provider credentials secure. You must be
                at least 18 years old to use the Service.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">4. SMS / Text Message Alerts</h2>
              <p>
                <strong>Program name:</strong> Creative Journey SMS Buy Alerts.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Program description:</strong> An optional alert program that sends you a text
                message when a stock on your Creative Journey watchlist or digest enters a "Buy"
                state. These are transactional alerts you request — we do not send marketing or
                promotional messages.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Opting in:</strong> You enroll by entering your mobile phone number and
                checking the consent box in your account settings. By opting in, you consent to
                receive recurring automated text messages from Creative Journey at the number
                provided.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Message frequency:</strong> Message frequency varies and depends on market
                activity and the tickers you follow.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Message and data rates:</strong> Message and data rates may apply. Check with
                your mobile carrier for details about your plan.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Opt-out:</strong> You can cancel the SMS service at any time by replying
                <strong>STOP</strong> to any message, or by turning off SMS alerts in your account
                settings. After you send <strong>STOP</strong>, we will send a confirmation message
                and then stop sending SMS alerts. You may receive an additional message confirming
                your request.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Help:</strong> For help, reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message, email
                <a href="mailto:support@creativejourney.com" class="text-primary-blue hover:text-primary-purple font-semibold">support@creativejourney.com</a>,
                or use the contact link from your account page.
              </p>
              <p>
                Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages. No mobile information
                will be shared with third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional
                purposes. Information sharing with subcontractors that support the service, such as
                our SMS provider (Twilio), is permitted solely to deliver the alerts you requested.
                See our
                <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary-blue hover:text-primary-purple font-semibold">Privacy Policy</a>
                for how we handle your data.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">5. Acceptable use</h2>
              <p>
                You agree not to misuse the Service, including attempting to disrupt or compromise its
                security, accessing data that isn't yours, scraping or overloading our systems, or
                using the Service for any unlawful purpose.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">6. Intellectual property</h2>
              <p>
                The Service, including its software, design, and content, is owned by Creative Journey
                and protected by applicable law. Content you create (such as your paper trades and
                notes) remains yours; you grant us a limited license to store and process it solely to
                operate the Service.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">7. Disclaimers</h2>
              <p>
                The Service is provided "as is" and "as available," without warranties of any kind,
                whether express or implied. We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted,
                error-free, or secure, or that any market data or signal is accurate.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">8. Limitation of liability</h2>
              <p>
                To the fullest extent permitted by law, Creative Journey will not be liable for any
                indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of
                profits or trading losses, arising from your use of the Service.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">9. Termination</h2>
              <p>
                You may stop using the Service and delete your account at any time from your account
                page. We may suspend or terminate access if you violate these Terms.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">10. Changes to these terms</h2>
              <p>
                We may update these Terms from time to time. When we do, we'll change the "Last
                updated" date and, for material changes, provide an in-app notice on your next
                sign-in. Continued use after the change constitutes acceptance.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">11. Contact</h2>
              <p>
                Questions about these Terms? Email
                <a href="mailto:support@creativejourney.com" class="text-primary-blue hover:text-primary-purple font-semibold">support@creativejourney.com</a>,
                or use the contact link from your account page.
              </p>
            </section>
          </div>

          <!-- Back Link -->
          <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-primary-blue hover:text-primary-purple font-semibold transition-colors"
            >
              ← Back to Home
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
